### User Context Memory System API Examples
### Use with REST Client extensions like VS Code REST Client

# Set base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001/api/v1
@contentType = application/json

### 1. Create User Preferences
POST {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/user123/preferences
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "preferences": {
    "tone": "professional",
    "style": "informative",
    "length": "medium",
    "complexity": "moderate",
    "language": "en",
    "targetAudience": "business professionals",
    "industry": "technology",
    "keywords": ["AI", "automation", "efficiency"],
    "avoidKeywords": ["outdated", "inefficient"],
    "customInstructions": "Focus on practical business applications and measurable results"
  }
}

### 2. Get User Preferences
GET {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/user123/preferences

### 3. Update User Preferences
PUT {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/user123/preferences
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "preferences": {
    "tone": "casual",
    "style": "conversational",
    "keywords": ["AI", "automation", "efficiency", "innovation"]
  }
}

### 4. Add Prompt History
POST {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/interactions
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "userId": "user123",
  "interactionType": "prompt",
  "data": {
    "stepId": "generate_output",
    "stepType": "generate_output",
    "stepName": "Generate Output"
  },
  "context": {
    "sessionId": "session_abc123",
    "metadata": {
      "workflowType": "seo_article"
    }
  },
  "outcome": {
    "success": true,
    "modifications": [],
    "satisfaction": 8
  },
  "timestamp": "2024-01-15T10:30:00Z",
  "duration": 5000,
  "metadata": {
    "contentType": "seo_article",
    "workflowType": "seo_article",
    "tokensUsed": 150,
    "cost": 0.003,
    "qualityScore": 8.5
  }
}

### 5. Get Prompt History
GET {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/user123/prompt-history?limit=10

### 6. Search Prompt History
GET {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/user123/prompt-history/search?query=AI%20automation

### 7. Analyze Prompt Trends
GET {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/user123/prompt-trends

### 8. Detect Behavior Patterns
POST {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/user123/behavior-patterns/detect

### 9. Get Behavior Patterns
GET {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/user123/behavior-patterns?patternType=time_preference

### 10. Personalize Content
POST {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/user123/personalize
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "content": "Artificial intelligence is transforming how businesses operate in the modern world. Machine learning algorithms are becoming increasingly sophisticated, enabling companies to automate complex processes and gain valuable insights from data.",
  "context": {
    "contentType": "seo_article",
    "workflowType": "seo_article"
  }
}

### 11. Adapt Prompt
POST {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/user123/adapt-prompt
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "prompt": "Write about AI in business",
  "context": {
    "workflowType": "seo_article"
  }
}

### 12. Check if Should Personalize
GET {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/user123/should-personalize?context={"contentType":"seo_article"}

### 13. Get User Insights
GET {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/user123/insights

### 14. Get Personalization Score
GET {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/user123/personalization-score

### 15. Get User Memory Stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/user123/stats

### 16. Add Content Feedback
POST {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/user123/content-preferences/seo_article/feedback
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "rating": 9,
  "feedback": "Excellent content with great structure and valuable insights",
  "aspects": ["clarity", "relevance", "depth", "usefulness"]
}

### 17. Get Content Preferences
GET {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/user123/content-preferences?contentType=seo_article

### 18. Get Interaction History
GET {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/user123/interactions?limit=20

### 19. Get Adaptation History
GET {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/user123/adaptations

### 20. Add Adaptation
POST {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/adaptations
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "userId": "user123",
  "adaptationType": "tone",
  "original": "The system processes data efficiently.",
  "adapted": "The system processes data with remarkable efficiency and precision.",
  "context": {
    "contentType": "seo_article"
  },
  "trigger": "automatic_detection",
  "effectiveness": 8.5,
  "confidence": 0.9,
  "timestamp": "2024-01-15T11:00:00Z"
}

### 21. Update User Configuration
PUT {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/user123/config
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "maxPromptHistory": 2000,
  "patternDetectionThreshold": 0.8,
  "personalizationEnabled": true,
  "autoAdaptation": true
}

### 22. Get User Configuration
GET {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/user123/config

### 23. Quick Personalize Content
POST {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/quick-personalize
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "userId": "user123",
  "content": "Machine learning is revolutionizing how we approach data analysis and decision making in modern businesses.",
  "contentType": "seo_article"
}

### 24. Quick Adapt Prompt
POST {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/quick-adapt-prompt
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "userId": "user123",
  "prompt": "Explain machine learning for beginners",
  "workflowType": "educational_content"
}

### 25. Search Users by Preferences
GET {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/users/search?preferences.tone=professional&preferences.language=en

### 26. Find Similar Users
GET {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/user123/similar?limit=5

### 27. Export User Data
GET {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/user123/export

### 28. Import User Data
POST {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/user456/import
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "preferences": {
    "userId": "user456",
    "preferences": {
      "tone": "casual",
      "style": "conversational",
      "language": "en",
      "keywords": ["AI", "technology", "innovation"]
    },
    "behaviorPatterns": {
      "frequentTopics": ["artificial intelligence", "machine learning"],
      "preferredStructures": ["introduction", "main points", "conclusion"],
      "commonModifications": ["add more examples", "simplify language"],
      "feedbackPatterns": ["improve clarity", "add depth"]
    },
    "adaptationHistory": [],
    "metadata": {
      "createdAt": "2024-01-15T00:00:00Z",
      "updatedAt": "2024-01-15T00:00:00Z",
      "lastInteraction": "2024-01-15T00:00:00Z",
      "interactionCount": 0,
      "adaptationCount": 0
    }
  },
  "promptHistory": [
    {
      "id": "prompt_1",
      "userId": "user456",
      "prompt": "What is AI?",
      "context": {
        "workflowType": "educational_content"
      },
      "response": "AI is a technology that enables computers to learn from data and make decisions.",
      "metadata": {
        "timestamp": "2024-01-15T10:00:00Z",
        "contentType": "educational_content",
        "workflowType": "educational_content",
        "tokensUsed": 50,
        "cost": 0.001,
        "qualityScore": 7.5
      }
    }
  ]
}

### 29. Batch Update Preferences
POST {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/batch/preferences
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

[
  {
    "userId": "user123",
    "preferences": {
      "tone": "professional",
      "style": "formal"
    }
  },
  {
    "userId": "user456",
    "preferences": {
      "tone": "casual",
      "style": "conversational"
    }
  }
]

### 30. Batch Add Interactions
POST {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/batch/interactions
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

[
  {
    "userId": "user123",
    "interactionType": "content_generation",
    "data": {
      "stepId": "generate_output",
      "stepType": "generate_output"
    },
    "outcome": {
      "success": true,
      "modifications": [],
      "satisfaction": 8
    },
    "timestamp": "2024-01-15T10:30:00Z",
    "metadata": {
      "contentType": "seo_article"
    }
  },
  {
    "userId": "user456",
    "interactionType": "prompt",
    "data": {
      "stepId": "generate_output",
      "stepType": "generate_output"
    },
    "outcome": {
      "success": true,
      "modifications": ["add more detail"],
      "satisfaction": 7
    },
    "timestamp": "2024-01-15T11:00:00Z",
    "metadata": {
      "contentType": "educational_content"
    }
  }
]

### 31. Cleanup Old Memory
POST {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/user123/cleanup?olderThanDays=30

### 32. Delete Old Prompt History
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/user123/prompt-history?beforeDate=2024-01-01T00:00:00Z

### 33. Delete Old Interaction History
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/user123/interactions?beforeDate=2024-01-01T00:00:00Z

### 34. Delete Old Adaptation History
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/user123/adaptations?beforeDate=2024-01-01T00:00:00Z

### 35. Delete Content Preferences
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/user123/content-preferences?contentType=seo_article

### 36. Delete Behavior Pattern
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/behavior-patterns/pattern_123

### 37. Delete User Preferences
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/user123/preferences

### 38. Get System Information
GET {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/info

### 39. Complex Workflow Example - Complete Personalization Flow

### Step 1: Create User Preferences
POST {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/user789/preferences
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "preferences": {
    "tone": "engaging",
    "style": "conversational",
    "length": "medium",
    "complexity": "moderate",
    "language": "en",
    "targetAudience": "youtube viewers",
    "industry": "entertainment",
    "keywords": ["entertaining", "educational", "viral", "engaging"],
    "avoidKeywords": ["boring", "technical", "academic"],
    "customInstructions": "Create content that is both entertaining and educational, suitable for YouTube audience"
  }
}

###

### Step 2: Add Initial Interaction
POST {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/interactions
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "userId": "user789",
  "interactionType": "prompt",
  "data": {
    "stepId": "generate_output",
    "stepType": "generate_output",
    "stepName": "Generate YouTube Script"
  },
  "context": {
    "sessionId": "youtube_session_123",
    "metadata": {
      "workflowType": "youtube_script"
    }
  },
  "outcome": {
    "success": true,
    "modifications": [],
    "satisfaction": 6
  },
  "timestamp": "2024-01-15T14:00:00Z",
  "duration": 8000,
  "metadata": {
    "contentType": "youtube_script",
    "workflowType": "youtube_script",
    "tokensUsed": 300,
    "cost": 0.006,
    "qualityScore": 6.5
  }
}

###

### Step 3: Personalize Content
POST {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/user789/personalize
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "content": "Today we're going to talk about artificial intelligence and how it's changing our world. AI systems can now write, create images, and even make decisions. This technology is advancing rapidly and affecting many industries.",
  "context": {
    "contentType": "youtube_script",
    "workflowType": "youtube_script"
  }
}

###

### Step 4: Add Feedback and Adaptation
POST {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/user789/content-preferences/youtube_script/feedback
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "rating": 8,
  "feedback": "Much better after personalization! The tone is more engaging and the content is well-suited for YouTube.",
  "aspects": ["tone", "engagement", "suitability"]
}

###

### Step 5: Add Adaptation Data
POST {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/adaptations
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "userId": "user789",
  "adaptationType": "tone",
  "original": "Today we're going to talk about artificial intelligence and how it's changing our world.",
  "adapted": "Hey everyone! Today we're diving into the fascinating world of artificial intelligence and how it's totally transforming our daily lives!",
  "context": {
    "contentType": "youtube_script"
  },
  "trigger": "personalization_request",
  "effectiveness": 8.5,
  "confidence": 0.9,
  "timestamp": "2024-01-15T14:30:00Z",
  "feedback": {
    "userRating": 8,
    "systemRating": 8.5,
    "comments": "Great improvement in engagement and audience suitability"
  }
}

###

### Step 6: Get Final Insights
GET {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/user789/insights

###

### Step 7: Get Final Personalization Score
GET {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/user789/personalization-score

