Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "context": {
    "contentType": "seo_article"
  }
}

### Test with invalid adaptation type
POST {{baseUrl}}/user-memory/adaptations
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "userId": "user123",
  "adaptationType": "invalid_type",
  "original": "Test content",
  "adapted": "Test adapted content"
}

### Test with invalid rating
